Class LocaleProjectStub

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable

    public class LocaleProjectStub
extends org.apache.maven.plugin.testing.stubs.MavenProjectStub
    The Maven Project stub file for testing the plugin new tag classes configuration. This stub is used to get the test and source file directories. This allows the TagList plugin unit tests run against the unit test directories instead of using the default project directories.
